msgstr "``Z_FACTOR``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1453
msgid "The factor exaggerates the height of the output elevation raster"
msgstr "El factor exagera la altura del ráster de elevación saliente"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1455
msgid "**Scale (ratio of vertical units to horizontal)**"
msgstr "**Escala (relación entre unidades verticales y horizontales)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1456
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2148
