msgstr "``SCALE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1460
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2152
msgid "The ratio of vertical units to horizontal units"
msgstr "El ratio de unidades verticales fente a unidades horizontales"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1461
msgid "**Azimuth of the light**"
msgstr "**Azimut de la luz**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1462
msgid "``AZIMUTH``"
msgstr "``AZIMUTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1465
msgid "Default: 315.0"
msgstr "Predeterminado: 315.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1466
msgid ""
"Defines the azimuth of the light shining on the elevation raster in degrees."
" If it comes from the top of the raster the value is 0, if it comes from the"
" east it is 90 a.s.o."
msgstr ""
"Define el acimut de la luz que brilla sobre el ráster de elevación en "
"grados. Si viene de la parte superior del ráster el valor es 0, si viene del"
" este es 90 a.s.o."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1470
msgid "**Altitude of the light**"
msgstr "**Altitud de la luz**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1471
msgid "``ALTITUDE``"
msgstr "``ALTITUDE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1474
msgid "Default: 45.0"
msgstr "Preestablecido: 45.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1475
msgid ""
"Defines the altitude of the light, in degrees. 90 if the light comes from "
"above the elevation raster, 0 if it is raking light."
msgstr ""
"Define la altitud de la luz, en grados. 90 si la luz proviene de arriba del "
"ráster de elevación, 0 si es luz rasante."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1484
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2165
msgid "**Use Zevenbergen&Thorne formula (instead of the Horn's one)**"
msgstr "**Usar la fórmula Zevenbergen&Thorne (en lugar de la de Horn's)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1490
