msgstr "**Sombreado combinado**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1491
msgid "``COMBINED``"
msgstr "``COMBINED``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1496
msgid "**Multidirectional shading**"
msgstr "**Sombreado multidireccional**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1497
msgid "``MULTIDIRECTIONAL``"
msgstr "``MULTIDIRECTIONAL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1502
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1562
msgid "**Hillshade**"
msgstr "**Sombreado**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1570
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:hillshade``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**: ``gdal:hillshade``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1580
msgid "Near black"
msgstr "Negro cercano"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1581
msgid "Converts nearly black/white borders to black."
msgstr "Convierte los bordes cercanos negros/blancos a negro."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1583
msgid ""
"This algorithm will scan an image and try to set all pixels that are nearly "
"or exactly black, white or one or more custom colors around the collar to "
"black or white. This is often used to \"fix up\" lossy compressed airphotos "
"so that color pixels can be treated as transparent when mosaicking."
msgstr ""
"Este algoritmo escaneará una imagen e intentará configurar todos los píxeles"
" que son casi o exactamente negros, blancos o uno o más colores "
"personalizados alrededor del cuello en blanco o negro. Esto se usa a menudo "
"para \"arreglar\" fotos aéreas comprimidas con pérdida de modo que los "
"píxeles de color puedan tratarse como transparentes al hacer mosaicos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1589
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL nearblack utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/nearblack.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Este algoritmo se deriva de la `utilidad GDAL nearblack "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/nearblack.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1613
msgid "**How far from black (white)**"
msgstr "**Como de lejos de negro (blanco)**"

